{
  "stem": "54.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the days when we worked, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were walking around, let's say, in the camp, not when you work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we were there and we were not working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But usually, we were working during the day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we came home in the evening, and we had to go right to bed to get to sleep.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were-- when we worked night shift, so we came 5 o'clock in the morning, so we had to go to sleep too, and be ready for the next hour to go back to work.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this-- this way, we didn't have much chance even to go out and to catch some fresh air.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But working, I was working with-- with my four girls, with-- the one who slept with me and the two who that slept above me on the bunker.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were, you know, always together, and each one-- each one of us was thinking about the next one, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all in the same shoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we try, you know, to be very friendly with each other and help each other as much as we could because this was the only way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, you wouldn't be able even to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Each of us, each-- each gave the next one a little bit support, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're talking maybe there's going to be a day when we're going to be free.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like this for the last-- like I said, a year there in that camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know too many people in this camp because we didn't have any very chance.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
